names.name: Jehovah Tzabaoth
names.description: The Divine Name associated with Netzach, emphasizing the enduring and victorious aspect of God.

names.name: Haniel
names.description: The Archangel associated with grace, charm, and the beauty found in endurance.

names.name: Elohim
names.description: The order of angels associated with Netzach, representing the multitude of divine creative forces.

names.name: Venus
names.description: The planetary influence associated with Netzach, symbolizing love, creativity, and attraction.

names.name: Nogah
names.description: Reflects the luminescence and brightness of divine victory and the triumph of light over darkness.

names.name: Nitzachon
names.description: Symbolizes the success and achievement that comes through perseverance and endurance.
